{"title":"Tarantulas on the Lifebuoy","author":{"name":"Thomas Lux"},"publishDate":"2012-01-28","lines":[{"line":"For some semitropical reason","stanza":1,"number":1},{"line":"when the rains fall","stanza":1,"number":2},{"line":"relentlessly they fall","stanza":1,"number":3},{"line":"into swimming pools, these otherwise","stanza":2,"number":4},{"line":"bright and scary","stanza":2,"number":5},{"line":"arachnids. They can swim","stanza":2,"number":6},{"line":"a little, but not for long","stanza":2,"number":7},{"line":"and they can’t climb the ladder out.","stanza":3,"number":8},{"line":"They usually drown—but","stanza":3,"number":9},{"line":"if you want their favor,","stanza":3,"number":10},{"line":"if you believe there is justice,","stanza":3,"number":11},{"line":"a reward for not loving","stanza":3,"number":12},{"line":"the death of ugly","stanza":4,"number":13},{"line":"and even dangerous (the eel, hog snake,","stanza":4,"number":14},{"line":"rats) creatures, if","stanza":4,"number":15},{"line":"you believe these things, then","stanza":5,"number":16},{"line":"you would leave a lifebuoy","stanza":5,"number":17},{"line":"or two in your swimming pool at night.","stanza":5,"number":18},{"line":"And in the morning","stanza":6,"number":19},{"line":"you would haul ashore","stanza":6,"number":20},{"line":"the huddled, hairy survivors","stanza":6,"number":21},{"line":"and escort them","stanza":7,"number":22},{"line":"back to the bush, and know,","stanza":7,"number":23},{"line":"be assured that at least these saved,","stanza":7,"number":24},{"line":"as individuals, would not turn up","stanza":7,"number":25},{"line":"again someday","stanza":8,"number":26},{"line":"in your hat, drawer,","stanza":8,"number":27},{"line":"or the tangled underworld","stanza":8,"number":28},{"line":"of your socks, and that even—","stanza":9,"number":29},{"line":"when your belief in justice","stanza":9,"number":30},{"line":"merges with your belief in dreams—","stanza":9,"number":31},{"line":"they may tell the others","stanza":9,"number":32},{"line":"in a sign language","stanza":10,"number":33},{"line":"four times as subtle","stanza":10,"number":34},{"line":"and complicated as man’s","stanza":10,"number":35},{"line":"that you are good,","stanza":11,"number":36},{"line":"that you love them,","stanza":11,"number":37},{"line":"that you would save them again.","stanza":11,"number":38}]}